[[Image:AB-parkland HWY.png|left|32px]]4 km east from Manly Corner (at the intersection with [[Alberta Highway 43|Highway 43]]) (located 35 km west of [[Edmonton, Alberta|Edmonton]]), Highway 16A runs parallel to Highway 16 to the south, through the communities of [[Stony Plain, Alberta|Stony Plain]] and [[Spruce Grove, Alberta|Spruce Grove]] into Edmonton, where it takes the name Stony Plain Road to its eastern terminus at [[Alberta Highway 216|Anthony Henday Drive]]. The road continues into [[downtown Edmonton]] as [[Stony Plain Road]]. On this section, called the '''Parkland Highway''', Highway 16A is a more leisurely alternative route to the corresponding section of Highway 16.
